                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-06-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 15, 1901</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Russell reports that information has been received by the President of
                    Venezuela that a war vessel of the United States has been anchored off the
                    island of Margarita, and that full details have been requested by the President
                    by cable of the governor of the island.)</p>
            </div>
